SetGlobal("GOOD","GLOBAL",-21)
ChangeAlignment(Protagonist,CHAOTIC_EVIL)~ + g-bbD000.main.quests.journal.pharod
CHAIN IF~~THEN g-bbD000 g-bbD000.main.quests.journal.pharod
@28 /*"Morte mentioned a name: Pharod. He also menioned a journal. Or were they multiple journals?" The zombie's hand tightens around your head. */
END
